snippet.title: The Gods Fabled: Soil Frontier - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
edit: now available in Indiegogo InDemand!: https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/the-gods-fabled-soil-frontier/x/29855105#/

The game has been funded on Kickstarter!: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/zoyji/the-gods-fabled-soil-frontier?ref=beandi

The Gods Fabled: Soil Frontier is now on Kickstarter! Support the campaign for an early discount, grab an Kickstarter-exclusive pet and maybe even design some in-game content.

Join the Discord community:  https://discord.com/invite/xWmt3cu5Ga
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/SoilFrontier
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SoilFrontier
